name: Ochako Uraraka | LoRA
description:
This is a LoRA of Ochako uraraka from MHA. This includes her hero outfit and school uniform.

To prompt her Hero Outfit I recommend using the keywords "urarakahero bodysuit". For the school uniform I recommend "u.a. school uniform, school uniform".

I haven't had much time to test if this works well with other models or not but for me a strength of 1 works good.

Do you like what I do? Feel free to support me on patreon
